organic_results.title: Nitrogen infused soluble cold brew instant coffee and process for preparation
organic_results.snippet: The present invention relates to a liquid coffee beverage comprising liquid coffee infused with nitrogen thus producing a refreshing cold foamy and creamy beverage.

organic_results.title: Foaming soluble coffee powder containing pressurized gas
organic_results.snippet: An instant coffee powder has dried soluble coffee in the form of particles or granules having internal voids filled with entrapped pressurized gas. Advantageously, when the coffee powder is dissolved in a beverage, the instant coffee powder produces a foam on the top surface of the beverage.
